    "start": 1564.8,
    "end": 1602.08,
    "text": "Thank you. Thank you for the information. I know this was put together in a rather quick timeline for a variety of reasons But I think it's really helpful to have an actual conversation about it. I have some questions and then some comments Is so looking at these options up here Are our staff required to attend these or do they choose to participate? Like for the police is it we need you to work this weekend because we have this event or is it there's an opportunity for overtime who would like to work and if not we can fill in with Herndon people or county people",
