    "turnId": "turn_000058",
    "start": 1764.28,
    "end": 1779.52,
    "text": "and I think It's important to say here that we have to follow our FLSA standards totally understand Yeah, and I know I just make clear from that perspective that exempt employees can work as many hours as we like Where hourly we certainly have to account for overtime and comp time.",
    "speaker": "Daniel Alexander"
